---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---
<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Interests</h1>
<section class="box skills mouse-move-smooth glass-border">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Full Stack Web Development</h2>
		<p>With expertise in PHP, Laravel, Vue.js, and MySQL, I excel in developing robust and scalable web applications. I bring a strong foundation in backend development, combined with frontend proficiency, to create seamless user experiences.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="trophy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Game Development</h2>
		<p>Utilizing engines like Unity (C#) and Unreal Engine (C++), I create captivating and immersive games. My passion for game development fuels my creativity, allowing me to design and implement engaging gameplay mechanics and stunning visuals.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Problem-Solving & Innovation</h2>
		<p>I am a quick learner and a collaborative team player. With five years of experience in the industry, I have honed my problem-solving skills and fostered a mindset of innovation. I thrive on tackling challenges and finding efficient solutions to create optimal outcomes.</p>
	</div>
</section>